snippet.title: Hotel Architect - Announcement Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Hotel Architect is a management simulation game that challenges players to build their very own hotel empire, as revealed during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022, by Publisher Wired Productions and developer Pathos Interactive - 

You can wishlist the game now on Steam by clicking here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1602000/Hotel_Architect/
